  Meksi also expresses his conviction that the affinity 
existing between the wing presided over by Berlusconi and the 
Albanian Government that he presently leads will be able to 
contribute to the traditional friendship that ties both peoples. 
  In his telegram, Meksi says: This makes me hope that this 
friendship will be raised to a higher level. I would like to 
hope that the generosity that Italy has shown toward Albania 
will continue and the close cooperation between both countries 
will be further strengthened for the common interest, ends the 
greeting telegram that Albanian prime minister has sent to Prime 
Minister Berlusconi on the occasion of the creation of the new 
Italian governmental cabinet. 

