<H3> <TI>   Sejm Speaker Receives PRC Army General </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sejm Speaker Receives PRC Army General </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1205182294 Warsaw PAP in Polish 1602 GMT 12 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1205182294 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>
<F P=105>  Polish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, 12 May--Sejm Speaker Jozef Oleksy today 
received General Zhang Wannian, chief of the General Staff of 
the Chinese People's Liberation Army, a Sejm Chancellery 
communique reads. 
  "While striving toward NATO and European structures' 
membership, we will not forget our good cooperation with China. 
Our countries have always respected their individual 
characteristics and their adopted solutions," the Sejm speaker 
said. 
  General Wannian, who is in Poland at the invitation of 
General Tadeusz Wilecki, chief of the General Staff of the 
Polish armed forces, shared his impressions of the visit. He 
stressed the good combat training of the Polish Army and the 
warm reception he encountered. He expressed the hope that 
Polish-Chinese relations will continue and that the visit of a 
Sejm delegation to China, scheduled for the end of May, will 
strengthen these relations, the communique reads. 

</TEXT>

