Dobrovsky." 
  "The strange management of state property, probably 
involving 
bribes and unjustified payments, are the best proofs of the 
character of not only Havel's collaborators, but of himself as 
well," the statement says. 
  According to the NKU report, the KPR made last year 
unsubstantiated payments amounting to 769,753 crowns (about 
$25,500) from its budget. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

