<H3> <TI>   Delegation Visits Military District </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Delegation Visits Military District </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1105165394 Warsaw PAP in English 1631 GMT 11 May 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> LD1105165394 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Bydgoszcz, May 11 -- A delegation of the Chinese 
People's liberation Army, headed by Chief of the General Staff 
General Zhang Wannian, visited the Pomeranian Military District 
(POW) on Wednesday, spokesman for the district commander Janusz 
Krzysztofik said. In Bydgoszcz, General Wannian met with 
Commander of the POW General Tadeusz Bazydlo to discuss the 
tasks and specific features of training in this district. The 
Chinese guest also visited the missile troops and Artillery 
Military Academy in Torun to get acquainted with the system of 
artillery officers' training. 

</TEXT>

