<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Federation Leaders To Be Elected at End of May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Federation Leaders To Be Elected at End of May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1305191494 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1730 
GMT 13 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1305191494 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb HTV Television </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Our reporter has just told us that a few minutes ago 
the Croatian and Muslim delegations ended their meeting held at 
the Croatian mission. They have agreed, among other things, to 
set up, within the next seven days, a commission in charge of 
missing persons. The commission will be set up on a parity 
basis. Toward the end of the month, the Constitutional Assembly 
of the Bosnia-Herzegovina federation will meet to elect the 
federation's president and prime minister, and pass several laws. 

