<H3> <TI>   Kanis on Troops for Former Yugoslavia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kanis on Troops for Former Yugoslavia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1305143894 Bratislava SLOVENSKY DENNIK in Slovak 9 May 94 
