<H3> <TI>   Patriarch Discusses Meeting </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Patriarch Discusses Meeting </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1605180294 Belgrade Radio Beograd Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 16 May 94 </F>

